The '''Eclipse''' was the most exclusive [[Hotel/Legends|hotel]] in [[Ussa]], the [[Capital/Legends|capital]] [[City/Legends|city]] of [[Bellassa/Legends|Bellassa]], with extraordinary service, catering to wealthy people.

The hotel had more than 200 floors with [[Transparisteel/Legends|transparisteel]] [[Turbolift/Legends|elevators]].

